Tested-by: Marco Franchi <marco.franchi@nxp.com>
Signed-off-by: Thierry Reding <treding@nvidia.com>
Link: https://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/msgid/20171011125958.23064-2-p.zabel@pengutronix.de

